          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Recognizing the Environmental Gains In Overcoming Negligence Act or the REGION Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits funds made available for any fiscal year from being used to close, consolidate, or eliminate an office of the Environmental Protection Agency, including a regional or program office.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        </item>
